TextBlock.Text: KICKASS: At last! We're here! the AAA variant! Watch out for the cracks in the ground.
BITCHASS: There's the engraving. Let's see, continues from the bottom right to the middle right and then all the way over to the middle left. And above it, a picture of-
BITCHASS: Another system. A picture of a small planet orbiting small star that is in turn orbiting a large black hole.
KICKASS: So we construct another warp gate by flying into the void again, like we did with this system?
BITCHASS: Bingo. Let's head to that black hole! I think we'll codename it Black.
